            <div class="title">
                India, Pakistan And Ceylon (Sterling Balances)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1950-12-07/debates/e7746b5f-17f1-4acd-913f-d33800823f4b/Korea(Operations)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
